sourcesContent: import React, { Component } from 'react' import { Segment, Item, Icon, Rating, Image, Grid, List } from 'semantic-ui-react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; class ItemListItem extends Component { render() { const { item } = this.props; return ( {item.name} {item.price} Category: {item.categories.map(category => ( category.title ))} {item.phone} {item.location.display_address} ) } } export default ItemListItem;
